      • getAppointmentsByCurrentMonth

        private void getAppointmentsByCurrentMonth()
        -LAMBDA- used to filter appointments by current month and reduces code, instead of using a traditional for loop. Set on the monthlyRadioButton - if selected, this method is called. Gets the current month and then creates a filtered list of appointments that consist of only appointments in that month. The list is then set as the tableview.

      • getAppointmentsByCurrentWeek

        private void getAppointmentsByCurrentWeek()
        Set on the weeklyRadioButton - if selected, this method is called. Gets the current week and then displays a list of appointments only in the current week. Sets the tableview to the list.

      • getAllAppointments

        private void getAllAppointments()
        Gets all the appointments and displays them.
